summary:
Early morning study session to the tune of computer architecture, my pumpkin candle, and Holy Ground 😊

Do you like to study at...
caption:
Early morning study session to the tune of computer architecture, my pumpkin candle, and Holy Ground 😊

Do you like to study at night or in the morning?
I find my productivity decreases a lot at night so I try to get up between 5 and 5:30 to get some studying in before class!

Huge motivator right now: knowing our girl Taylor is working on new music - if she’s on the grind I should be too!!

imma just give everyone a lil bit of context on this

sooo if y’all don’t know, I’m graduating in less than 5 months so we obviously have a yearbook that requires a write up, a quote and a unique superlative (something that you want people to remember you for)

I obviously asked my friends for help because I didn’t want to label myself as something I’m actually not (ya know what I mean?) anyways, they gave me that: walking taylor swift encyclopedia because I have established myself to be That Taylor Swift Girl

and I am: DOWN FOR IT!!! WHAT DO U GUYS THINK???
